{"tid":1932071,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"<國屍> 陳雲：《願榮光歸香港》之後，香港人變成全世界憎恨的愚民","createTime":"2020-03-18T13:35:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T02:37:12.000Z","uid":227801,"like":8,"dislike":112,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"a11e74a9550bcfa224fce280ace1c7e6e72fcc90","tid":1932071,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:35:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/df5kurV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdf5kurV.jpg&h=ccdabecf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：《願榮光歸香港》之後，香港人愚昧自大，認為自己防疫有功，高舉香港微生物學家的個人崇拜，譴責西人不衛生。<br />\n這首歌是褻瀆上天的，觸犯神明的，招來厄運的，令香港人當自己是神。當時很多耶穌教會在推廣這首歌！我當初為什麼批評這首深層國家輔助流行的泛民黃絲歌，正是因為它可以將一百多年的國際城市人民變成現在全世界憎恨的愚民，方便共產黨接收香港。<br />\n二十幾間商場出場地給黃絲大合唱。大家今日見到後果。<br />\n集體催眠，mass hypnosis。泛民做的，共產黨出主意，泛民黃絲代勞，香港人繼續支持泛民吧，最後自己無處立足。"},{"pid":"1bc4e27fc5988fd190c803b09dea00578c9f9350","tid":1932071,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:37:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0dc0755ca47ddf0981363a630d6147b5aa00a3","tid":1932071,"uid":23169,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:38:13.000Z","msg":"條廢老唔抵得首歌紅過佢香港城邦歌"},{"pid":"57fb791873767148ca1419f7ac282365f5b29550","tid":1932071,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:39:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fSAMp2M.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfSAMp2M.gif&h=0e3fbf37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f2de3459662d70f4353caf04ac8da3c107d5234","tid":1932071,"uid":227801,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"4f0dc0755ca47ddf0981363a630d6147b5aa00a3","tid":1932071,"uid":23169,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:38:13.000Z","msg":"條廢老唔抵得首歌紅過佢香港城邦歌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T13:39:48.000Z","msg":"點止&quot;紅過&quot;咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" clas